rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Ain't no one in Gula who knows
more about bugs than me! Ask away!

rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0007
rows.name:
Wait a second... You can find those
pretty much anywhere in Gula!

rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0008
rows.name:
Everybody knows that!
Come on, don't waste my time...

rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0010
rows.name:
I've never caught one before.
You sure you're not making it up?
You're pulling my leg?

rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0011
rows.name:
I guess I can't say for sure they don't
exist... I'll have to study some more.

rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0013
rows.name:
You can find them out past Hermit's
Hollow toward Coolley Lake.
